  "description": "This table provides information about classification societies, which are organizations that establish and maintain technical standards for the construction and operation of ships and other marine structures. It includes details such as the name, abbreviation, founding date, head office location, and membership status in the International Association of Classification Societies (IACS). The table is useful for understanding the key attributes and affiliations of these organizations.",
